   <text:p text:style-name="P49"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P49">Alors, M<text:span text:style-name="Police_20_par_20_dÃ©faut"><text:span text:style-name="T59">me</text:span></text:span>Â Josserand posa carrÃ©ment la question Ã  lâoncle.</text:p>
